                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18400203-578-offence-1 t18400203-cd-21"></join>18th of January</rs>, 40 yards of carpet, value 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 18<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18400203-name-202" type="victimName">
